px] flex-1 px-8 pb-24 pt-12 md:px-20 md:pt-14\"><div class=\"mb-12 rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8\"><p class=\"max-w-4xl text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-lg\">Operating generation in Taplejung and a feasibility-stage pipeline spanning Taplejung and Panchthar — figures aligned to company-context.md.</p></div><div class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/90 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8 [&amp;_strong]:font-semibold [&amp;_strong]:text-brand-blue\"><section class=\"py-28 first:pt-10\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-8 w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">Upper Phawa Khola</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-heading text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-brand-blue lg:text-5xl\">Operational generation</h2></div></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-5 lg:items-center lg:gap-24\"><div class=\"relative min-h-[420px] overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/60 bg-white shadow-sm lg:col-span-2\"><img alt=\"Project site photo placeholder — Upper Phawa Khola headworks and powerhouse\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1509395176047-4a66953fd231%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/35 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center lg:col-span-3\"><h3 class=\"font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue md:text-3xl\">Upper Phawa Khola (5.8 MW)</h3><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-xl font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8\">Upper Phawa Khola is an operating run-of-river plant in Taplejung. Company disclosures record COD on <strong>BS 2081/01/08</strong>, with a Pelton configuration and an intertie to Amarpur substation.</p><div class=\"mt-10 max-w-xl rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-slate/50\">Fact sheet</p><dl class=\"mt-5 grid gap-5 text-sm md:grid-cols-3 md:text-base\"><div><dt class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Capacity</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 font-heading text-lg font-bold tabular-nums text-brand-blue md:text-xl\">5.8 MW</dd></div><div><dt class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">COD</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 font-semibold tabular-nums text-brand-slate\">BS 2081/01/08</dd></div><div><dt class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Turbine</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 font-semibold text-brand-slate\">2 × Pelton</dd></div></dl></div><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-xs leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/60\">Note: the ~22 km, 132 kV transmission line in disclosures applies to Middle Iwa (feasibility), not this operating intertie.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-slate-200/60 bg-glacier-mist py-28\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-8 w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">Middle Iwa Khola</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-heading text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-brand-blue lg:text-5xl\">Development pipeline</h2></div></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-5 lg:items-center lg:gap-24\"><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center lg:order-1 lg:col-span-3\"><h3 class=\"font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue md:text-3xl\">Middle Iwa Khola (15 MW)</h3><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-xl font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-[17px] md:leading-8\">Middle Iwa Khola remains a feasibility-stage run-of-river project in Taplejung and Panchthar. Disclosures highlight the planned<!-- --> <strong>~22 km, 132 kV</strong> transmission line and an ownership structure with <strong>51%</strong> held by Unitech Hydropower, alongside a first-year revenue estimate of<!-- --> <strong>NPR 51.15 Cr</strong>.</p><div class=\"mt-10 max-w-xl rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm\"><p class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-slate/50\">Fact sheet</p><dl class=\"mt-5 grid gap-5 text-sm md:grid-cols-3 md:text-base\"><div><dt class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Capacity</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 font-heading text-lg font-bold tabular-nums text-brand-blue md:text-xl\">15 MW</dd></div><div><dt class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Ownership</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 font-semibold tabular-nums text-brand-slate\">51%</dd></div><div><dt class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Transmission</dt><dd class=\"mt-2 font-semibold text-brand-slate\">~22 km, 132 kV</dd></div></dl></div></div><div class=\"relative min-h-[420px] overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/60 bg-white shadow-sm lg:order-2 lg:col-span-2\"><img alt=\"Engineering schematic placeholder — Middle Iwa Khola\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 50vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1559136555-9303baea8ebd%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1559136555-9303baea8ebd%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1559136555-9303baea8ebd%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1559136555-9303baea8ebd%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1559136555-9303baea8ebd%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1800%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-15591365